        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "As soon as morning morrowed, he donned his clothes and taking the dinars, repaired to the story teller, whom he found seated at the door of his house.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
