        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258290/8590_258290_000009_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "\"And do ye not worship him?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258290_000009_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258290/8590_258290_000009_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "\"We worship the Sun, and prostrate ourselves thereto.\" \"O Wazir Faris, the sun is but a star of the stars created by Allah (extolled and exalted be He!), and Allah forbid that it should be a Lord!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258290_000009_000021",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258290/8590_258290_000009_000021.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "So he abode in cark and care and chagrin from morn to night and from night to morn.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258290_000009_000024",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258290/8590_258290_000009_000024.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "Will any save a stranger take it?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "When it was the Seven Hundred and Sixty third Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "Alas!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000005_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000005_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "What?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000005_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000005_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "Are all of you impotent to cure my son?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000005_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000005_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "Except ye heal him forthright, I will put the whole of you to death.\" The Archiater replied, \"O King of the Age, in very sooth we know that this is thy son and thou wottest that we fail not of diligence in tending a stranger; so how much more with medicining thy son?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000005_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000005_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "What is this portrait whereof thou art enamoured?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000005_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000005_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "And why didst thou not tell me.\" He replied, \"O my sire, I was ashamed to name this to thee and could not bring myself to discover aught thereof to any one at all; but now thou knowest my case, look how thou mayest do to cure me.\" Rejoined his father, \"What is to be done?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000005_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000005_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "If I find trace or tidings of her, my wish will be won, and if not, belike the voyage will broaden my breast and recruit my courage; and haply by foreign travel my case will be made easy to me, and if I live, I shall return to thee safe and sound.\"--And Shahrazad perceived the dawn of day and ceased to say her permitted say.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "When it was the Seven Hundred and Sixty fourth Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000007_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000007_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "Then he fell to buffeting his face and would have cast himself into the sea, but his Mamelukes withheld him, saying \"O King, what will this profit thee?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000007_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000007_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "Thou hast brought all this on thyself; for, hadst thou hearkened to thy father's words, naught thereof had betided thee.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000007_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000007_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "But this was written from all eternity by the will of the Creator of Souls.\"--And Shahrazad perceived the dawn of day and ceased saying her permitted say.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "When it was the Seven Hundred and Sixty fifth Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "And indeed, at the time of thy birth, the astrologers assured thy sire that all manner troubles should befal thee. So there is naught for it but patience till Allah deliver us from this our strait.\" Replied the Prince, \"There is no Majesty and there is no Might save in Allah, the Glorious, the Great!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "Neither is there refuge nor fleeing from that which He decreeth!\" And he sighed and recited these couplets,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "\"By the Compassionate, I'm dazed about my case for lo!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "Then he became drowned in the depth of thoughts and his tears ran down upon his cheeks like torrent rain; and he slept a while of the day, after which he awoke and sought of food somewhat.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "It drifted with them at the will of the winds and the waves, night and day a great while, till their victual was spent and they saw themselves shent and were reduced to extreme hunger and thirst and exhaustion, when behold, suddenly they sighted an island from afar and the breezes wafted them on, till they came thither.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "Then, making the cock boat fast to the coast and leaving one therein to guard it, they fared on into the island, where they found abundance of fruits of all colours and ate of them till they were satisfied.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000011_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000011_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "Presently, they saw a person sitting among those trees and he was long faced, of strange favour and white of beard and body.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000011_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000011_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "Come, tarry with us and we will mount on your backs and give you meat and drink, and you shall be our donkeys.\" Hearing this they hastened the more seawards till they left them in the distance and fared on, trusting in Allah Almighty; nor did they leave faring for a month, till another island rose before them and thereon they landed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000011_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000011_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "Here they found fruits of various kinds and busied themselves with eating of them, when behold, they saw from afar, somewhat lying in the road, a hideous creature as it were a column of silver.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8590_258292_000011_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8590/258292/8590_258292_000011_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8590",
        "content": "So they climbed to the top and there saw a thick copse.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
